metadata.name: FACE ARMOR GOLD #001
metadata.description:
Golden Demon Mask

Metaverses are now gaining great popularity, in this regard, I decided to create my own collection of masks. I wanted to do something similar to a fashion show, I hope I succeeded.
People hide behind masks in real life, and I want to give them the opportunity to hide in virtual life as well.
The owner of the token receives:
1. Optimized mask model for use in your own metaverse.
2. Detailed model for 3D printing.
3. Original video in high quality.
